.DT
delalt
Discworld creator help
delalt


.SH Name
.SI 5
delalt - Deletes a name from the player's list of alt characters.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
delalt <player_name> <alt_name> [<alt_name> ...]
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This commands deletes a name from the player's list of alt character. The
player whose list is being modified should be marked as "main". Please refer
to the "addalt" command description for more information.
.EP

.SH Notes
.SP 5 5
1. This command can be very CPU-intensive, especially when many alt character
names are specified.
.EP
.SP 5 5
2. This is a restricted command: only senior creators and lords can use it.
.EP

.SH Examples:
.SI 5
> playerinfo fiona
Report for: Fiona aka Belcar, Mayhem

> playerinfo belcar
Report for: Belcar (alt of Fiona)

> delalt fiona belcar griffin
Deleted Belcar from Fiona's list of alts.
Couldn't delete: Griffin.

> playerinfo fiona
Report for: Fiona aka Mayhem

> playerinfo belcar
Report for: Belcar
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
playerinfo, addevent, delevent, addalt
.EP
